`addCraft [shortcut] [iLvl]` - add a craft that you have available, uses the craft shortcut
`removeCraft [shortcut] [iLvl]` - remove a craft from your list once used
`myCrafts` - get a list of crafts you currently have
`listCrafts {page}` - get a list of crafts with shortcut and description (limited to 10 per page)
`isCraftShortcut [shortcut]` - check if a value is a valid craft shortcut
`findCraft [shortcut] {iLvl} {page}` - search crafts by shortcut and iLvl limited to 10 per page, use the page parameter to show later pages
`setPoEIGN [ign]` - set your IGN for contact whispers generated by this bot
`craftwhisper [@discordusername] [shortcut] [iLvl]` - Get a whisper to contact the craft owner in-game

* Legend: Parameters wrapped in [] are required, wherease parameters wrapped in {} are optional